---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Galaxy";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Galaxy</h1>
    <span class="badge">Avnish Kumar Thakur (Developer)</span>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        As a student at PICT, I embody a blend of curiosity and diligence, underpinned by a resolute work ethic. Renowned for my unwavering dedication and commitment to tasks, I am often sought out for my leadership potential within collaborative endeavors. Beyond excelling in competitive coding, I continuously seek opportunities to refine my skills and empower those around me.
    </p>
    <p>
        My leadership extends beyond technical prowess, fostering an inclusive and supportive environment where teamwork thrives. Through genuine kindness and approachability, I cultivate a culture of mutual respect and encouragement. By embracing the diverse strengths of my peers, I drive collective progress toward our shared goals, leaving an indelible mark as a diligent team player and inspiring leader.
    </p>
    <div class="center">
        <a href="/works/">
            <button class="btn">My portfolio</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="skills center">
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="C++" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/cplusplus/cplusplus-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="React" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/react/react-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Node js" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/nodejs/nodejs-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Python" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Bootstrap" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/bootstrap/bootstrap-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Git" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"/>
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        Apart from my passion for coding, I am deeply enthusiastic about sports and exploring new destinations through travel. I am committed to maintaining a holistic approach to my well-being, ensuring both mental and physical fitness remain integral parts of my lifestyle.
    </p>
</Layout>

